codex
The cache validation is timestamp-based, and the stale bugs are real: the LSP/compiler can read virtual editor text while the cache validates against disk mtimes. I’m going to patch the scoped file-access layers so cache metadata sees a synthetic mtime derived from the active editor snapshot/version.
